    "name": "OLAPU",
    "steam_appid": 3331590,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >OLAPU 是一款节奏超快的合作动作类 Roguelite 游戏，你最多可以和三位朋友组队，一起迎战越来越疯狂的敌人浪潮和庞大的团队副本式 Boss。每一轮游戏都是一场生存与成长的竞速，是你们是否有资格挑战这个世界最强存在的终极证明。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3331590/extras/2519e15dd290d43957b3279dc8e23b18.avif?t=1762380089\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3331590/extras_big/2519e15dd290d43957b3279dc8e23b18.webp?t=1762380089 width=1600 height=200 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >近战、远程、辅助、纯输出？你想怎么玩都行。OLAPU 提供多种独特角色可供选择，每位角色都有专属的攻击方式、技能和终极技。玩得越久，角色越强大，还会解锁改变战斗风格的特殊升级。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3331590/extras/214d89bb7d0630b1d8d01e407c6790a1.poster.avif?t=1762380089\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3331590/extras/214d89bb7d0630b1d8d01e407c6790a1.webm?t=1762380089\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3331590/extras/214d89bb7d0630b1d8d01e407c6790a1.mp4?t=1762380089\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3331590/extras/c0cbefc1554428ec771452c99ff3f9c2.avif?t=1762380089\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3331590/extras_big/c0cbefc1554428ec771452c99ff3f9c2.webp?t=1762380089 width=1600 height=200 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >击败敌人后会掉落星星，你可以将它们兑换成星座碎片，解锁各种强力效果：召唤技能、疯狂的连锁反应，甚至还有一个小猫赌场等你探索！每一轮都有数十种选择，没有任何一次体验是重复的。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3331590/extras/f470298bad0c184013e724b3e909d44c.poster.avif?t=1762380089\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3331590/extras/f470298bad0c184013e724b3e909d44c.webm?t=1762380089\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3331590/extras/f470298bad0c184013e724b3e909d44c.mp4?t=1762380089\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3331590/extras/364eaaa1b5199a7be767afc594477de1.avif?t=1762380089\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3331590/extras_big/364eaaa1b5199a7be767afc594477de1.webp?t=1762380089 width=1600 height=200 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Boss 设计灵感来自 MMO 团队副本。它们拥有多个阶段，需要不停移动，容错率极低。想要活下来，你必须读懂攻击节奏，掌握机制并快速适应。这些战斗不仅考验你个人的反应，还需要团队全员高度专注。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3331590/extras/2b58f07cc0967732caa77804e9330da1.poster.avif?t=1762380089\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3331590/extras/2b58f07cc0967732caa77804e9330da1.webm?t=1762380089\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3331590/extras/2b58f07cc0967732caa77804e9330da1.mp4?t=1762380089\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3331590/extras/fe3ff8a13c818eb52ca79c85f1542000.avif?t=1762380089\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3331590/extras_big/fe3ff8a13c818eb52ca79c85f1542000.webp?t=1762380089 width=1600 height=200 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每次游戏之间，你都可以解锁新角色和他们的进阶形态，获得永久性技能强化，找到拥有随机属性的传奇装备，通过食物提升下一轮战斗的 Buff，并为你和角色解锁各种炫酷外观。无论胜负，每一次尝试都会让你更进一步。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3331590/extras/4c717ca725dce549d14eb44285a7c380.poster.avif?t=1762380089\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3331590/extras/4c717ca725dce549d14eb44285a7c380.webm?t=1762380089\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3331590/extras/4c717ca725dce549d14eb44285a7c380.mp4?t=1762380089\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
